## üõ†Ô∏è VS Code Extension

Get real-time autocorrection as you type!

### Features
- ‚úÖ Syntax highlighting
- ‚úÖ IntelliSense autocomplete
- ‚úÖ Error detection
- ‚úÖ Manual correction (`Ctrl+Shift+F`)
- üöß Ghost text suggestions (coming soon)

### Install

```bash
cd vscode-extension
code --install-extension .
```

